         <abstract>
            <p>An algorithm is presented for the computation of the $n$ zeros of the polynomial $q_n$ having the property that $q_n(t) \exp (-t)$ alternates $n$ times, at the maximum value 1, on $\lbrack 0, + \infty)$. Numerical values of the zeros and extremal points are given for $n \leqq 10$.</p>
          </abstract>
